📝 Conclusion

The Pickle Rick room is an excellent starting point for beginners in ethical hacking. It introduces core concepts like enumeration and command execution in a fun and engaging way.

By completing this lab, you gain hands-on experience in:

Web exploitation basics
Linux command-line usage
CTF methodology
